**Website Template**
=====================

A basic website template using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.

**Getting Started**
---------------

### Prerequisites

* A web browser (e.g. Google Chrome, Mozilla Firefox)
* A code editor (e.g. Visual Studio Code, Sublime Text)

### Installation

1. Clone the repository: `git clone https://github.com/your-username/website-template.git`
2. Open the project folder in your code editor
3. Open the `index.html` file in your web browser

**Features**
--------

* Responsive design using CSS media queries
* Navigation menu with links to different sections
* Hero section with background image and call-to-action button
* About section with text and image
* Services section with list of services
* Contact section with form and submit button
* Footer with copyright information

**Technologies Used**
-------------------

* HTML5
* CSS3
* JavaScript (for interactive elements)

